%h1 Moe Vocab Cards
%form.well
  %label
    :markdown
      This page takes a list of simplified or traditional Chinese words and turns them into Anki cards with the @@@.
  %h3 Word List
  %textarea.span7#mvc-words(rows="8" placeholder="Add words here, separated by newlines.")

  <br><br>

  %a.btn.btn-primary#mvc-lookup Look up words

  <br><br>

  %textarea.span7#mvc-output(rows="8" placeholder="The generated flashcards will appear here ready for import to Anki after you've added all the words and clicked on \"Look up Words\".")

  %textarea.span7#mvc-not-found(rows="8" placeholder="The words that are not in the dictionary will appear here.")




